SliTaz RPi
================================================================================


SliTaz Raspberry Pi distro tools and files


Spi quickstart
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The Raspberry Pi have a lot of specification SliTaz ARM provide 'spi' to build
custom SliTaz Rpi distro's images ready to boot. To get the list of avalaible 
commands and options:

# spi help

Slitaz RPi mirror host the prebuilt Linux kernel package. To get the
latest version and unpack it:

# spi get-linux

The 'gen' command will generate a new SliTaz Raspberry Pi distro using 'sat'.
I will also install needed firmware and boot configuration files.

# spi gen

